<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="split-v">split <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /splɪt/    美 /splɪt/  </p>
<p>(split, split)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(使) 分裂；(使) 分开：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The branch split under their weight.
树枝在他们的重压下断裂了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Split</strong> the pineapple <strong>down the middle</strong>.
把菠萝从中间切开。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>分担；分摊：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We share a house and split all the bills.
我们合住一所房子，分摊所有费用。</p></div></div>